## 1. 🔐 OTP Authentication (Replace Mock)

**Current state:** Any 6-digit code is accepted. OTP is logged to console.

**What to build:**

| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| OTP Provider Integration | MSG91 / Twilio / Gupshup — send real SMS |
| OTP Storage | Redis/KV store: key = `otp:{mobile}`, value = hashed OTP, TTL = 5 min |
| OTP Verification | Compare submitted OTP against stored hash |
| Rate limiting on send | Max 3 OTP requests per mobile per 10 min |
| Rate limiting on verify | Max 5 attempts per OTP session, then block |
| OTP expiry | Auto-expire after 5 minutes |
| Resend logic | Allow resend only after 30s cooldown (already in UI) |

**Env vars needed:**
```
OTP_PROVIDER=msg91
MSG91_AUTH_KEY=<key>
MSG91_TEMPLATE_ID=<template_id>
MSG91_SENDER_ID=<sender>
REDIS_URL=<redis-connection-string>
```

