## 2. 🎨 AI Image Generation Service

**Current state:** Mock 1.8s delay, returns hardcoded designs.

**What to build:**

| Component | Details |
|-----------|---------|
| Generation API route | `POST /api/ai-cake-studio/generate` |
| Prompt engineering | Combine user prompt + style + occasion + flavor + zodiac into optimized provider prompt |
| Provider integration | OpenAI DALL-E 3 / Stability AI / Midjourney API / Replicate |
| Image storage | Upload generated images to S3/Cloudflare R2/Supabase Storage |
| Response shape | Return array of 2–3 image URLs + metadata |
| Timeout handling | 30–60s max wait, graceful timeout error |
| Retry logic | 1 automatic retry on provider failure |
| Fallback | If provider is down, return error state (don't deduct credits) |

**API contract:**

```ts
// POST /api/ai-cake-studio/generate
// Request
{
  prompt: string
  style: string
  occasion: string
  flavor: string
  zodiacInfluence?: { sign: string; suggestion: string }
  imageCount?: number // default 3
}

// Response (success)
{
  success: true
  generationId: string
  designs: [
    {
      id: string
      imageUrl: string
      title: string       // AI-generated or derived
      description: string // AI-generated
      style: string
    }
  ]
  creditsRemaining: number
}

// Response (failure)
{
  success: false
  error: string
  code: "QUOTA_EXHAUSTED" | "RATE_LIMITED" | "PROVIDER_ERROR" | "AUTH_REQUIRED"
  creditsRemaining?: number
}
```

**Env vars needed:**
```
AI_PROVIDER=openai          # or "stability" or "replicate"
OPENAI_API_KEY=<key>
AI_IMAGE_STORAGE=r2         # or "s3" or "supabase"
R2_ACCOUNT_ID=<id>
R2_ACCESS_KEY=<key>
R2_SECRET_KEY=<secret>
R2_BUCKET_NAME=cake-designs
R2_PUBLIC_URL=https://cdn.crossfriend.in
```

