## 4. 🛡️ Rate Limiting & Abuse Protection

**Current state:** None.

**What to build:**

| Layer | Rule |
|-------|------|
| Per-user cooldown | 1 generation every 20–30 seconds |
| Per-user daily cap | Max 5 generations/day (free tier) |
| Per-IP rate limit | Max 10 requests/minute to generation endpoint |
| In-flight lock | `generation_locked = true` while request is processing; reject duplicates |
| Device fingerprint (optional) | Prevent multi-account abuse from same device |
| Honeypot (optional) | Detect bot patterns |

**Implementation options:**
- Redis-based rate limiter (recommended)
- Vercel Edge middleware rate limiting
- Upstash Redis (serverless-friendly)

